sql:
SELECT overall_rating
FROM player_ratings
WHERE year = '2013';

SELECT first_name || ' ' || last_name AS full_name
FROM players
ORDER BY full_name;

SELECT AVG(crossing) AS average_crossing_skill
FROM technical_skills
WHERE year = '2013';

SELECT MAX(overall_rating) AS highest_rating
FROM player_ratings
WHERE year = '2013';

external_knowledge:
- A player is considered to be currently with a team if they have an active contract;
- The most recent season is determined by the latest season end date;
- Two years is equivalent to 730 days.
